Package: mesh-desktop
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libsecret-1-0
Maintainer: Mesh maintainers
Description: Native Mesh operator console
 Mesh Desktop is the unprivileged administration client for a remote Mesh
 control plane. It does not install or run the managed node service.
